###Shortcuts:
###You can replace the value you obtain for 
###“token,” “noteId,” and “username” in these
###variables to test the endpoints more easily. 

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
@noteId = YOUR_NOTE_ID_HERE
@username = YOUR_USERNAME_HERE

### ==========================================
### AUTHENTICATION ENDPOINTS
### ==========================================

### 1. Register a new user
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "AdminUser",
  "email": "admin@braindump.dev",
  "password": "SecurePassword123!",
  "role": "ADMIN"
}

### 2. Login
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@braindump.dev",
  "password": "SecurePassword123!"
}

### 3. Forgot Password (Triggers email with reset link)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@braindump.dev"
}

### 4. Reset Password (Requires token from email)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "USER_ID_FROM_EMAIL",
  "token": "TOKEN_FROM_EMAIL",
  "newPassword": "NewSecurePassword123!"
}

### ==========================================
### NOTES ENDPOINTS
### ==========================================

### 5. Get all notes (Supports pagination & filtering)
GET {{baseUrl}}/notes?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Create a new note
POST {{baseUrl}}/notes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "My First Note",
  "content": "<p>This is the content of my note, saved via API.</p>",
  "tags": ["documentation", "api"]
}

### 7. Generate an AI draft using Gemini
POST {{baseUrl}}/notes/draft
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "topic": "The SOLID principles in object-oriented programming"
}

### 8. Update an existing note
PUT {{baseUrl}}/notes/{{noteId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "My Updated Note",
  "content": "<p>Updated content.</p>",
  "tags": ["documentation", "updated"],
  "isFavorite": true
}

### 9. Delete a note
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/notes/{{noteId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. Get all unique tags used by the authenticated user
GET {{baseUrl}}/notes/tags
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ==========================================
### ADMIN ENDPOINTS (Requires ADMIN role)
### ==========================================

### 11. Get user profile details
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/{{username}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 12. Get all notes from a specific user
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/{{username}}/notes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}